name: Tammy Wyble
text: Dr. Kunz is a great doctor and a good listener.  He takes his times and explains things thoroughly.  Their offices are run efficiently and my appointment wait times are always reasonable.

name: Marcia Gillian
text: Dr. Kunz is one of the best physicians I have had. He is genuinely concerned about his patients, and takes time to listen and to address all questions. I highly recommend him!

name: Joni King
text: Dr. Kunz is very professional, knowledgeable and thorough. Each of my visits has been at ease and precise. The team of nurses are. very friendly and will assist patients when needed!

name: Andrea Seright
text: Dr Kunz is amazing! I been seeing him about 10 years now and he never disappointed me. He takes time out to listen and he cares. My visits are always pretty fast with no long wait. He does not rush out the room , he take time and listen. My husband, started going to see him and he is so happy also! I love Dr Kunz and highly recommended him!!!

name: Loretta Jones
text: I have been going to Dr.Kunz for 3 1/2 years and He is a great professional Dr.He doesn't waist time,you have everything you need before you leave,tech's are great to,if you call they always call you back and that means a lot to me and if lab results are not right they will give you a call as well.

name: Laurie Franklin
text:
I did not like the fact that I had to wait almost 2 hours.  I was told the reason was because I was late and that was not true!!!  My appointment time was 8:30 and I arrived at 8:20!!  I think what happened was I have new insurance and after they updated everything that’s when I was checked in!!!

On a positive note, I was very impressed with getting my lab results back the same day!!!

name: JANITA GERMANY
text:
I love Dr.Kunz, I have been going to him for years now.
He gets u in and out..
Very Satisfied Patient..

name: Dorothy Rembert
text: My overall experience at Seale Harris Clinic was excellent.  The staff was very informative and ready to assist.

name: Christine Gibson
text: I love the fact that you don't have to wait a long period of time to be seen by the doctor. I so appreciate my doctor's concerns for me.

name: Brent Holcombe-Fluker
text: All my needs were met in a extremely timely fashion. Dr. Kunz and his staff got me back on the right track with my concerns & medication , & I am extremely grateful.

name: Crombie's World
text: Great bed side manners!

name: Aaron Ingram
text: Attentive doctor and polite staff.

name: Joy Bittle
text: Fast. and top the point

name: Brendella Reddock
text: Dr. Kunz is very friendly and great at what he does. First visit and I selected him as my PCP. No need to look any further. He's taking good care of me.

name: Kristyn Taylor
text:
I love Dr. Kunz! His bedside manner is very solicitous and kind, he really listened to all my concerns, he answered all my questions, and (unlike a lot of doctors) he didn't make any abrupt changes to my meds at my first visit with him.  Also, the clinic is great and all the ladies in the office are super sweet.
I have finally found a new PCP!

name: Shakina Dixon
text: Omg I have the best primary physician in the world! Dr. Kind is open, honest, and he us very good at his job..i refer everyone to him. He's awesome and so is his staff..go check him and his folks out people..they get the job done and u feel better. And they're all so sweet and respectful..

name: cynthia kizzire
text: Dr. Kunitz is the best. Always pleasant and the office is run like a well oiled machine.

name: Amanda Warnix
text: He's a great Dr...  One of the best!

name: Missy Powell
text: Nice place with very fast, professional services. Hope they get enough referrals to stay in business in Prattville. Recommend you getting your Imaging services, including same day MRI, at this facility as you can usually choose where you want to go yourself! Utilize this place as we want to keep a place this nice in our "Preferred Community"!

name: Jonathan Eric Headley
text: Very nice facility. Easy to get to very nice and professional staff. Always easy to talk to and help in anyway possible. They try everyway to make you comfortable. I went in January 2018 for an MRI and I am about to have another one. I am requesting Sonos Imaging. They even have snacks and drinks for their patients. If I could give more stars I would.

name: Leslie Pettway
text: Really nice staff and the office and customer changing room was beautiful.
